rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0001
rows.name:
A pleasure to make your acquaintance.
My name is Kinakina, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0002
rows.name:
My father told me the Mercenary Group was getting busy
and asked me to come and help, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So, do you know where my father is, mo?
I need to see him quickly, or there will be trouble, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0004
rows.name:
On the way here, I angered an Igna with an eyepatch
who had a lightning-element Blade, so I think he'll
be here soon, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0005
rows.name: That was probably Thunder-Rending Zeke... mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0006
rows.name:
I hear he has a move called the Tyrant's Evil Eye that can
kill people just by making eye contact, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0007
rows.name:
This might be a crisis that could destroy Hr√¶svelgr,
but I'm sure my father will do something about it, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0008
rows.name:
Mo-mo?!
You'll do something about it instead of
my father, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300041_01_msg0009
rows.name:
That's wonderful, mo!
Then I'll leave it in your capable hands, mo.
